title: 01/07/21 - HOUR 3 - Mike Florio
itunes:title: 01/07/21 - HOUR 3 - Mike Florio
description:
The guys wrap up the final hour of the Dan Patrick Show discussing more details of what took place in Washington D.C. Then Mike Florio calls into the show talk about the NFL's upcoming postseason, Rams Vs Seahawks and how much longer he thinks Jarred Goff will be suiting up for the LA Rams.
